data.title: 19-Year-Old Justin Timberlake Shows Off His Tennessee Hometown In Access Hollywood Throwback
data.meta_description: There's no place like home for Justin Timberlake! Twenty years ago, the then-19-year-old music superstar gave Access Hollywood a tour of his Tennessee elementary school and shared details about his childhood. Then, three years later, Justin invited Access to nearby Memphis and some of its landmarks, including the famous Sun Studios.
